```js
const helmet = require('helmet');
app.disable('x-powered-by');
app.use(helmet());
```

### 2. No rate limiting / brute-force protection (A04: Insecure Design, A07: Auth Failures)
`/users` and `/health` are unauthenticated and uncapped. Even `/health` can be abused for amplification or probing.

**Fix:**
```js
const rateLimit = require('express-rate-limit');
app.use(rateLimit({ windowMs: 60_000, max: 100, standardHeaders: true, legacyHeaders: false }));
