### 2. Missing security headers (OWASP A05: Security Misconfiguration)
No `helmet`, so responses leak `X-Powered-By: Express` and omit `Content-Security-Policy`, `Strict-Transport-Security`, `X-Content-Type-Options`, etc.

**Fix:**
```js
const helmet = require('helmet');
app.disable('x-powered-by');
app.use(helmet());
```

