### 🟡 6. Body parser / payload size not configured (OWASP A04)

No `express.json()` is registered today, but as soon as one is added without a limit, the default in modern Express is 100kb — you should still set it explicitly, and reject non-JSON content on JSON endpoints.

```js
app.use(express.json({ limit: '16kb', strict: true }));
// Reject unexpected content types on POST/PUT/PATCH when you add them.
```

