### 🟡 9. Server binds to all interfaces; no HTTPS enforcement (OWASP A05)

`app.listen(3000)` binds to `0.0.0.0`. Usually correct behind a load balancer, but if you terminate TLS at the app you'll want to enforce HTTPS and HSTS (helmet does HSTS). Also consider binding host explicitly when appropriate:

```js
