### 🟡 10. No structured request logging (OWASP A09)

`console.log` on startup only. For any prod deployment you want per-request logs with a correlation ID, and you want to ensure logs don't capture `Authorization` headers, cookies, or request bodies.

```js
const pino = require('pino-http')({
