### 5. **No global error handler / request timeout** (OWASP A09: Logging & Monitoring failures, A05)

**Severity: Low**

Any thrown error bubbles to Express's default handler, which in development mode leaks stack traces. There is also no request timeout, so slowloris-style clients can tie up sockets.

