| OWASP category | Why it doesn't apply here |
|---|---|
| **A03 Injection** (SQLi, NoSQLi, command inj.) | No user input is read; no DB; no `exec`/`child_process`; no template rendering. |
| **SSRF (A10)** | No outbound HTTP calls. |
| **XSS** | No HTML rendering; only JSON responses. Content-Type is set correctly by `res.json`. |
