1. Add auth to `/users` (fix #1).
2. Add `helmet` + disable `x-powered-by` (#2).
3. Add rate limiting (#3).
4. Add global error handler and server timeouts (#5).
5. Split `app.listen` out of `app.js` (#7).
6. Make host/port configurable and front with TLS (#6).
